snippet.title: Archero by Habby - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out our latest title - Archer+Hero = ARCHERO!

Battle as the lone archer trying to defeat and escape all forms of evil as you crawl your way through dungeons in different worlds. Experience a multitude of skill combinations; each unique and fun!

Just remember, once you die, you'll have to start from the beginning!

Download now and play for free at:
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/sg/app/archero/id1453651052?mt=8
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.habby.archero

Check out more information on:
https://habby.fun
